## Storage Limits

### Platform Limits

| Platform | Approx. Limit | Mitigation |
|----------|---------------|------------|
| iOS (UserDefaults) | 1 MB | Use for small config only |
| iOS (Core Data/SQLite) | Device-dependent | Monitor usage; prune old data |
| Android (SharedPreferences) | 1 MB | Use for small config only |
| Android (Room/SQLite) | Device-dependent | Monitor usage; prune old data |

### Storage Budget

- [ ] Define max storage per data type (e.g., 50 MB for cache)
- [ ] Implement LRU eviction when limit reached
- [ ] Prune sync metadata older than retention window
- [ ] Log storage usage in diagnostics

### Eviction Checklist

- [ ] Eviction policy documented (LRU, TTL, manual)
- [ ] User data is never evicted without user action
- [ ] Eviction does not corrupt data integrity
- [ ] Eviction runs in background; does not block UI

